snippet.title: Underworld Ascendant Out Now on PlayStation 4 (PEGI)
snippet.description:
Play Underworld Ascendant Now on PlayStation 4 and Coming Soon to Xbox One! Enter The Stygian Abyss, a dangerous, highly interactive dungeon world. Mix and match dozens of combat, stealth and magic skills to develop your own unique style of play. Set out on more than 70 quests, earn rewards and unlock skills through resourceful, unboxed gameplay and ingenious performance. Become The Ascendant.

For behind the scenes details on all of 505's games, head to the official 505 Games Blog: http://www.505games.com/blog
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/505Games
Twitter: https://twitter.com/505_Games
